title: Control Denied - The Fragile Art Of Existence
description:
Control Denied was a band formed by Chuck Schuldiner( Death ) to create progressive heavy metal, mixed with elements of power and death metal. The band started in 1996 as Schuldiner wanted to procure a more melodic style than was possible with Death.
